if (age < 16) 
  System.out.println("Cannot get a driver's license");
else 
  System.out.println("Can get a driver's license");
```

**III:**
```java
if (age < 16) 
  System.out.println("Cannot get a driver's license");
else if (age >= 16) 
  System.out.println("Can get a driver's license");
```

**IV:**
```java
